snippet.textDisplay:
Coke studio never fails to impress. I have so much respect for Zohaib kazi and Ali hamza for having such a revolutionary approach.
Extremely excited to see krewella, Vishnu, ariana and amrina, ahad mir raza, sounds of kolachi, lyaari underground, Mughal e funk, NAGHMA AND LUCKY ( SO PROUD OF YOU) , chand tara orchestra and also great to see abrar ul haq and jawad ahmad back in action.❤❤❤
This season is going to be remarkable because other than the ppl i've mentioned above we also have other great musicians of Pakistan taking part in this beautiful project.❤
Sorry that was long 😅 😅😅
